<h2>Overview</h2>

<p>A grand total of three themes are currently available. With no preference for dark mode or high contrast, the <strong>light</strong> theme is chosen for the user by default. It's probably the one you are currently in contact with.</p>

<p>Setting the <code>data-theme</code> attribute on a container element will style its content according to your desired theme. Available values are:</p>
<ul>
  <li><code>light</code></li>
  <li><code>dark</code></li>
  <li><code>a11y</code></li>
</ul>

